Title: BuildStats.info - BuiltWithDot.Net
Description: BuildStats.info is an open RESTful API which can generate SVG widgets for displaying build history charts and NuGet/MyGet badges in public Git repositories. It currently supports build history charts for AppVeyor, TravisCI and CircleCI builds.

Title: Statement on New York Times Article
Azure Functions Updates Include Moving .NET Outside the Runtime
Description: Azure Functions is moving to an out-of-process model that runs a .NET worker process alongside the runtime. The Azure Functions team also announced public preview support for Node.js 14, general availability of custom handlers and Java based functions running on Linux in its January update.

Title: MySqlConnector - BuiltWithDot.Net
